<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>New property listed on Death is a Deadline</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      background-color: #0d0d0d;
      color: #e8e2d9;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #141414;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      padding: 32px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header .brand {
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #c9a96e;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: normal;
      color: #f0ebe3;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 36px 40px;
    }
    .body p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #b0a899;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .property-card {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .property-card .label {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #6b6258;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .property-card .name {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #f0ebe3;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .property-card .location {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #7a7068;
    }
    .cta-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #c9a96e;
      color: #0d0d0d;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 20px 40px 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4a4540;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <p class="brand">Death is a Deadline</p>
      <h1>A new property has been added<br/>to your account.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>
        An administrator has listed a new property under your account on Death is a Deadline.
        You can now manage its availability, set your minimum bid, and track bookings from your dashboard.
      </p>

      <div class="property-card">
        <p class="label">New Property</p>
        <p class="name"><%= placeName %></p>
        <p class="location"><%= placeCity %>, <%= placeCountry %></p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Head to your dashboard to review the listing details, update availability, 
        and configure your bidding preferences.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-wrapper">
        <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta">Go to My Dashboard</a>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <p>
        If you believe this was added in error, please contact our support team.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Death is a Deadline &mdash; Student accommodation bidding platform</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
